data.description: This amazing Beazer home features high ceilings, an open floor plan, wrought iron spindles, and a covered patio for outdoor entertaining and leisure. Take your culinary abilities to the next level in the gorgeous island kitchen, equipped with granite countertops, a mosaic backsplash, walk-in pantry, and pendant lighting. The private master suite features a walk-in closet, dual vanities, tub, and separate shower. Enjoy easy commutes to the Medical Center and Downtown Houston via Highway 288. Explore nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment at Pearland Town Center. The amenities of Bluewater Lakes include a recreation area with a park, swimming pool, and playground. Schools are zoned to Alvin ISD. Ask the Beazer New Home Consultant about our top of the line SPRAY FOAM insulation!
